biography: Martin Seeler supercharges global supply chains with GenAI as Sr Staff AI Engineer at Blue Yonder. He ships AI that survives angry customers, skeptical executives, and Black Friday traffic. Speaks globally about the messy reality of production AI. Measures success in customer value delivered.
